-- Mexico Equity Movers: Alpek, Fibra Uno, Urbi, America Movil, Geo
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   L e v i n
-- 2013-04-03T23:23:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-03/mexico-equity-movers-alpek-fibra-uno-urbi-america-movil-geo.html
IPC index fell 0.9% at 3pm in Mexico
City trading.  ADVANCERS:
* Aeroportuario del Pacifico (GAPB MM) +2.1%; rose to highest in
a month on closing basis
* Alfa (ALFAA MM) +1.8%; co. said after mkt closed its Sigma
unit bought Costa Rica cheese producer Empresas Monteverde
* Alpek (ALPEKA MM) +1.4%
* Fibra Uno (FUNO11 MM) +1.3%; CS analysts led by Vanessa
Quiroga recommended buying co.’s shrs on upside potential,
according to e-mailed report  DECLINERS:
*  America Movil  (AMXL MM) -1.8%; Miguel Barbosa, head of PRD in
Mexico’s Senate, said yday in e-mailed statement that changes to
telecom bill should be resolved in next 2 weeks
* Geo (GEOB MM) -4%
* Urbi (URBI* MM) -3.1%
* Cemex (CEMEXCPO MM) -3.6%; biggest drop since Feb. 7  To contact the reporter on this story:
